EN: This enterprise has been monopolizing the local market.
ZH: 这个行业的几家大型企业都在竞争独占市场份额。
EN: Several large corporations in this industry are competing to dominate the market share.
ZH: 那个独家协议使他们独占了该地区的分销渠道。
EN: That exclusive agreement allows them to have exclusive control over the distribution channels of that area.
ZH: 他儿子总是独占玩具，不肯分享。
EN: His son always takes exclusive possession of the toys and refuses to share.
ZH: 该公司为了独占市场，进行了大量的广告投放。
EN: The company carried out a lot of advertising campaigns in order to monopolize the market.
