EN: The enemy has completely monopolized the supply of goods in this area.
ZH: 这个品牌独占了整个市场的高端消费者。
EN: This brand monopolizes the high-end consumers in the entire market.
ZH: 他们企图通过独占知识产权来削弱竞争对手。
EN: They attempted to weaken their competitors by monopolizing intellectual property rights.
ZH: 这本杂志独占了行业内的市场份额。
EN: This magazine holds the market share exclusively within the industry.
ZH: 这个国家的媒体完全被政府独占了。
EN: The media of this country is completely monopolized by the government.
